WEBVTT

1
00:16:49.110 --> 00:16:51.270 
Amy 即使对你来说 这都太下作了
Amy, this is low, even for you.

2
00:16:51.280 --> 00:16:55.480 
难以置信 你们两个都违反了"留在楼下"的规矩
I cannot believe you would both violate the "Please stay downstairs" Rule,

3
00:16:55.480 --> 00:16:57.340 
我明明再三强调过的
Which was prominently posted!

4
00:16:57.340 --> 00:16:58.870 
快出去
Get outta here!

5
00:16:58.870 --> 00:17:01.420 
我不知道为什么还要谈这事
I don't know why we have to have this discussion again.

6
00:17:01.420 --> 00:17:02.270 
怎么办
What do we do?

7
00:17:02.270 --> 00:17:04.520 
卫生间 卫生间
Bathroom! Bathroom.

8
00:17:07.290 --> 00:17:08.720 
你为何生我的气
Why are you upset with me?

9
00:17:08.730 --> 00:17:11.030 
你的下属才是派对上最扫兴的人
Your employees are the ones putting a damper on the party.

10
00:17:11.030 --> 00:17:12.260 
他们表现糟透了
They are acting terribly.

11
00:17:12.260 --> 00:17:13.770 
你才是那个表现糟糕的人
You're the one who's been acting terribly tonight.

12
00:17:13.770 --> 00:17:15.730 
对我的客人一副敷衍 自以为是的态度
You've been curt and snobby with my guests.

13
00:17:15.730 --> 00:17:17.600 
你一直在刺激(针织)Peralta
You've been needling poor Peralta so much,

14
00:17:17.600 --> 00:17:19.300 
都快能给他织出来一套新衣服了
You've practically made him a new suit.

